descriptionHtml:
This mod turn Broken Oar Grotto into a player home, in the way of maing all containers non respawning, i am thinking of later spicing it up a bit with some extra deco but i think that ill maybe just let it stay as it is, as i quite like it allready


There wont be any pictures as i dont want to spoil the dungeon for thoose who havent already comepleted it
